Kailangan niyang lumipat ng tatlong beses.

786
00:39:17,000 --> 00:39:18,320
Nakatira ang kanyang pamilya sa Chang Island.

787
00:39:18,840 --> 00:39:20,560
Para kang isang tunay na detektib.

788
00:39:20,840 --> 00:39:21,560
Mga babae lang

789
00:39:21,560 --> 00:39:22,880
magkaroon ng pang-anim na pandama

790
00:39:23,440 --> 00:39:24,600
tungkol sa bagay na ito.

791
00:39:24,960 --> 00:39:25,920
Sino ang malapit kanino,

792
00:39:25,960 --> 00:39:26,760
sino ang hindi nagkakasundo,

793
00:39:26,760 --> 00:39:27,840
mararamdaman mo lang.

794
00:39:28,400 --> 00:39:29,240
Kaya dapat ba nating ibigay kay Shi Min

795
00:39:29,240 --> 00:39:30,160
tumawag at magtanong?

796
00:39:30,360 --> 00:39:31,240
Oo, tatawagan ko siya ngayon.

797
00:39:37,800 --> 00:39:38,960
Hello? Qing Ye?

798
00:39:39,720 --> 00:39:40,520
Hi, Shi Min.

799
00:39:40,960 --> 00:39:42,200
Nakipag-ugnayan ka na ba kay Big G?

800
00:39:42,440 --> 00:39:44,680
Kasama ko siya ngayon.

801
00:39:47,920 --> 00:39:50,040
Pakipadala agad ang iyong lokasyon.

802
00:39:50,280 --> 00:39:51,520
Galit na galit ang nanay ni Big G.

803
00:39:51,520 --> 00:39:52,560
Nagpunta pa nga siya sa pulis.

804
00:39:54,000 --> 00:39:54,600
Tara na.

805
00:39:55,120 --> 00:39:55,720
Paano tayo nakakarating doon?

806
00:40:00,600 --> 00:40:01,360
Kaya mo bang maglayag?

807
00:40:01,600 --> 00:40:03,080
Huwag husgahan ang isang libro batay sa pabalat nito.

808
00:40:03,320 --> 00:40:04,680
Lahat ng nandito sa Zhazhating

809
00:40:04,680 --> 00:40:05,680
marunong maglayag ng bangka.

810
00:40:08,600 --> 00:40:09,200
Tara, alis na tayo.

811
00:40:09,720 --> 00:40:10,400
Sige, Kapitan.

812
00:40:18,720 --> 00:40:19,360
Kumapit nang mahigpit.

813
00:40:20,120 --> 00:40:20,680
Tara na.

814
00:40:37,280 --> 00:40:37,880
Salamat.

815
00:40:37,880 --> 00:40:39,160
Binabawi namin ang ulat.

816
00:40:39,840 --> 00:40:40,760
Bilisan mo.

817
00:40:41,200 --> 00:40:42,040
- Anong papasok?
- Bilis, bilis.

818
00:40:42,560 --> 00:40:43,240
Dahan-dahanin.

819
00:40:43,760 --> 00:40:45,120
Sumama ka sa akin. Nasa Chang Island siya.

820
00:40:45,280 --> 00:40:46,720
Paano mo nalaman

821
00:40:46,720 --> 00:40:47,680
nandoon ba siya?

822
00:40:47,720 --> 00:40:49,040
May narinig akong mga taong nag-uusap sa tawag niya.

823
00:40:49,080 --> 00:40:49,760
Binanggit nila

824
00:40:50,280 --> 00:40:52,000
mga sakahan at talaba.

825
00:40:52,600 --> 00:40:53,920
Chang Island lang ang nandito

826
00:40:53,960 --> 00:40:55,080
may mga sakahan ng talaba.

827
00:40:55,240 --> 00:40:56,040
Oo.

828
00:40:56,240 --> 00:40:57,680
Pero napakalaki ng isla.

829
00:40:57,720 --> 00:40:59,000
Pupunta ba tayo sa bahay-bahay?

830
00:40:59,200 --> 00:41:01,400
Gagawin ko kung kinakailangan.

831
00:41:02,240 --> 00:41:02,920
Kasalanan ko lahat 'to.

832
00:41:02,920 --> 00:41:04,560
Hindi ko dapat siya pinagalitan kahapon.

833
00:41:05,160 --> 00:41:06,320
Ang mga batang lalaki ay pinapagalitan paminsan-minsan,

834
00:41:06,320 --> 00:41:07,520
hindi naman malaking bagay 'yun.

835
00:41:07,880 --> 00:41:08,240
Ako...

836
00:41:08,880 --> 00:41:11,200
Sinaktan ko pa nga siya.

837
00:41:11,720 --> 00:41:13,240
Ginawa mo?

838
00:41:14,080 --> 00:41:15,760
Tinapik ko ang likod niya,

839
00:41:15,960 --> 00:41:16,760
tinapik ang kanyang ulo

840
00:41:16,760 --> 00:41:17,920
at hinila ang kanyang mga tainga.

841
00:41:18,640 --> 00:41:19,440
Wala lang 'yan.

842
00:41:19,520 --> 00:41:21,120
Hindi 'yan maituturing na pambubugbog sa pamilya ko.

843
00:41:22,160 --> 00:41:23,120
May mga masasakit din akong sinabi.

844
00:41:23,880 --> 00:41:24,800
"Nauutal ka"

845
00:41:24,800 --> 00:41:25,760
"sobra."

846
00:41:25,760 --> 00:41:27,000
"Sinong babae ang magkakagusto sa'yo?"

847
00:41:27,120 --> 00:41:28,080
"Kung hindi ka mag-aaral nang mabuti,"

848
00:41:28,080 --> 00:41:28,880
"Ano na ang mangyayari sa iyo?"

849
00:41:32,960 --> 00:41:33,840
Ginawa ba ng mga salitang iyon

850
00:41:33,920 --> 00:41:35,240
nasaktan nang husto ang pride niya?

851
00:41:35,880 --> 00:41:36,560
Oo.

852
00:41:38,400 --> 00:41:39,360
Nag-aalala ako na baka may gawin siyang kalokohan,

853
00:41:40,240 --> 00:41:41,240
parang tumalon sa dagat.

854
00:41:42,360 --> 00:41:43,120
Huwag kang magsalita ng walang katuturan.

855
00:41:43,360 --> 00:41:43,840
Yufen.

856
00:41:44,680 --> 00:41:45,880
Hindi ba ang asawa mo

857
00:41:45,880 --> 00:41:46,440
madalas maglayag papuntang Chang Island?

858
00:41:47,440 --> 00:41:48,120
Oo, ginagawa niya.

859
00:41:48,600 --> 00:41:49,680
Bumalik sa Zhazhating Pier

860
00:41:49,760 --> 00:41:50,400
ngayon din.

861
00:41:50,560 --> 00:41:51,880
Maaari niya tayong ihatid sakay ng bangka.

862
00:41:51,880 --> 00:41:52,240
Tara na.

863
00:41:52,880 --> 00:41:53,720
Bilisan mo.

864
00:41:54,040 --> 00:41:54,800
Hintayin mo ako.

865
00:41:54,920 --> 00:41:56,000
Tara na.

866
00:41:56,080 --> 00:41:56,520
Naku!

867
00:42:02,120 --> 00:42:02,520
Teka.

868
00:42:03,160 --> 00:42:03,960
Nasaan ang bangka?

869
00:42:04,200 --> 00:42:05,920
Oo, nasaan na?

870
00:42:06,560 --> 00:42:06,920
Naku, hindi.

871
00:42:07,200 --> 00:42:07,800
Naku, kalokohan!

872
00:42:08,080 --> 00:42:09,040
Nawala na rin ang mga susi.

873
00:42:09,320 --> 00:42:10,200
Seryoso, sino?

874
00:42:10,480 --> 00:42:12,400
Sino ang kumuha ng bangka natin?

875
00:42:12,440 --> 00:42:13,520
Hindi ko man lang

876
00:42:13,560 --> 00:42:14,800
kailangan mag-isip.

877
00:42:15,040 --> 00:42:16,040
Dapat anak mo 'yan.

878
00:42:16,080 --> 00:42:16,960
Kinuha niya ito.

879
00:42:17,080 --> 00:42:17,800
Kyle.

880
00:42:18,000 --> 00:42:19,880
Hahabulin kita sa susunod na linggo!

881
00:42:20,080 --> 00:42:20,760
Tara na.

882
00:42:20,960 --> 00:42:21,640
Sakay na lang kayo ng ferry.

883
00:42:21,760 --> 00:42:22,200
Bilisan mo.

884
00:42:22,400 --> 00:42:22,720
Sige.

885
00:42:22,760 --> 00:42:23,160
Tara na.

886
00:42:23,240 --> 00:42:24,200
Mahal, bumalik ka na sa trabaho.

887
00:42:24,240 --> 00:42:24,960
Alis na kami.

888
00:42:57,520 --> 00:42:58,400
Malapit na tayo.

889
00:43:13,080 --> 00:43:13,920
Napakalaki ng lugar na ito.

890
00:43:17,600 --> 00:43:18,480
Mag-ingat.

891
00:43:29,880 --> 00:43:31,520
Napakalaki at siksikan dito.

892
00:43:31,560 --> 00:43:32,120
Pasensya na, pasensya na.

893
00:43:32,560 --> 00:43:34,040
May mga taong ganap na natatakpan.

894
00:43:34,040 --> 00:43:35,080
Paano natin siya mahahanap?

895
00:43:35,880 --> 00:43:36,600
Nagtanong-tanong na ako.

896
00:43:37,000 --> 00:43:38,240
Ito mismo ang sakahan ng mga pagkaing-dagat

897
00:43:38,240 --> 00:43:38,800
pinapatakbo ng pamilyang Shi.
